title: Use .3ish Eth to Deploy Community Airdrop
body:
MultiSender.app needs roughly .33 ETH to deploy 500 HYP to the Registered Users on 31/12/2020
Requesting Use of Bounce Event Funds to Deploy the airdrop to the community with strategy to replace before liquidity lock event on uniswap.
